1
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:49,160
We made it.

2
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:50,560
We made it! We made it!

3
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:54,720
We made it!

4
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:56,440
Wait.

5
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:57,800
Wait a second.

6
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:01,720
What did the host just say?

7
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:03,000
He said we made it.

8
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:03,800
No, no.

9
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,290
The part after that.

10
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:08,560
The finals will be decided by online and offline audience voting.

11
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,080
Right.

12
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,080
The part before that.

13
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,039
Before that.

14
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:17,800
The champion team wins a cash prize of 100,000.

15
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,160
Enter the semi-finals,

16
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,520
become the champion.

17
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:27,240
Didn't you say we'd get 100,000 just for making the semi-finals?

18
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,880
What about the debt to Liu Ma?

19
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:40,039
How could I have missed those words?

20
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,000
I...

21
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:43,560
It's nothing.

22
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,440
It's my own problem.

23
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,840
I have to solve it myself.

24
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,930
You guys just get ready for the finals.

25
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,440
Are you back?

26
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,440
Not yet. I've got something to do here.

27
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,440
You know those songs I wrote?

28
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,480
Check for me in the next couple of days

29
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,320
to see if anyone wants them.

30
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,200
If anyone does,

31
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,240
sell them all.

32
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,880
People offered high prices before,

33
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,800
but you wouldn't sell those treasures.

34
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:27,530
What's wrong? Is your uncle still short on money?

35
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,760
I can't explain it in a few words.

36
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,200
Anyway, just remember to do that.

37
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:33,600
I'm not selling the songs anymore. Thanks.

38
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,860
I'll talk to you later.

39
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:44,180
I can handle it myself.

40
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,000
Brother.

41
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,040
Take this.

42
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,960
It's all my fault.

43
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,960
I didn't read the ad clearly.

44
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,200
It's okay.

45
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,480
Qiuqiu, listen to me.

46
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,400
The drum shop owner just paid me for the classes.

47
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,080
Take it.

48
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,120
20,000.

49
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,160
I don't have any more right now.

50
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:15,880
Besides,

51
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,440
I should be paying you interest anyway.

52
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,130
Just consider it a loan.

53
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,360
I'm touched.

54
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,400
Brother, really, there's no need.

55
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,600
Come on, let's take a picture.

56
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:48,260
You can come to me for money anytime with the IOU.

57
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,800
Hold it up.

58
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:55,880
Come on.

59
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,640
It's a deal then.

60
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:21,040
We'll let you get back to work. We're off.

61
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:21,600
Okay.

62
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:22,680
I'll walk you out.

63
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,480
The contract.

64
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,960
The tea garden signed ten commercial performances with us,

65
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,620
and they can pay us in advance.

66
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,610
Brother, go coordinate with them.

67
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,680
Anan.

68
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,480
You've got quite a head for business.

69
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,800
The money Liu Ma needs isn't a problem anymore.

70
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,520
Jealous?

71
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:36,880
Why are you getting so cocky?

72
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,540
Come on, praise me.

73
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,280
You did...

74
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,200
just okay.

75
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,800
Sit down.

76
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,240
Brother, look.

77
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,120
So many people like us.

78
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,700
There are tens of thousands of comments.

79
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,880
For the online voting in the finals,

80
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,010
we have a chance now.

81
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,159
Wait, Brother.

82
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,040
Why are you so calm?

83
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,300
Don't tell me it's you.

84
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,450
No need to see me out.

85
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,520
Take care. Bye.

86
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,000
Old Wang.

87
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,060
I'm not selling songs.

88
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,940
Don't you have a bunch of video accounts?

89
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,920
I'll send you the videos in a bit.

90
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,880
Liu Ma, you're awesome.

91
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,040
But,

92
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:37,840
Bro,

93
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:40,690
isn't this the kind of stuff you hate the most?

94
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,880
I posted you guys.

95
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,240
I didn't post myself.

96
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,880
Brother, don't be shy to admit it.

97
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,960
You just love us.

98
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,800
There are so many comments.

99
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,200
Look.

100
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:12,960
They say I'm handsome.

101
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,520
No, no.

102
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,100
I have to find one about me.

103
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,920
Come and look.

104
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,200
This one.

105
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,420
What's wrong, Qiuqiu?

106
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,600
I feel like

107
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,280
you're different from when you first arrived.

108
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,360
I just feel like

109
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,690
I should do something for the band.

110
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,159
Join us on stage for the finals, Zona.

111
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:33,640
Join us on stage for the finals.

112
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:33,800
Anan will be very happy.

113
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,460
Anan will be very happy, Zona.

114
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,370
I'll leave the competition to you.

115
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,120
Hurry up, you two.

116
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,040
Coming.

117
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,800
Music should speak through talent.

118
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,720
We can accept the result, win or lose.

119
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,400
We don't need your dirty tricks

120
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,460
to help us advance.

121
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,640
From this moment on,

122
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:00,600
you're fired.

123
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,120
Do it.
